	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/05/19/morning-agenda-atts-move-for-directv/" data-title="AT&#038;T&#8217;s Move for DirecTV" data-description="AT&amp;T has agreed to buy DirecTV for $48.5 billion. | AstraZeneca has rejected Pfizer&#039;s &quot;final&quot; offer. | Google may buy the video game service Twitch. | Deutsche Bank plans to raise fresh capital.">
